40|$|The {{increasing}} {{ubiquity of}} sensors embedded in products enables innovative <b>business</b> <b>logics</b> in physical industries: value is co-created and exchanged among multiple organizations in a collaborative ecosystem. However, current means of business model design and analysis mainly offer an organizational centric perspective. By adopting a design science approach, we develop {{a model to}} represent business models in physical industries from an ecosystem perspective. In this research in progress, focused of the automotive industry, we describe the first cycle of problem identification and artifact design, as well as further steps in our approach...|$|R
