40|$|Find the <b>business</b> <b>logics</b> {{that drive}} the main field of {{recycling}} of used clothing should not throw into discouragement the environmental awareness of our citizens, {{attentive to the}} improvement of the ecosystem. Every year in Italy, is disposed about one hundred thousand metric tons of textiles: the authors outline the ideal path from the moment when, emptied the wardrobes and put the packages in the collection bins, they come to the treatment plant devoted to the processes of recovery or recycling. The technical procedures for carrying out these activities and places resale complete the topic, while also providing possible critical insights...|$|R
